\c 37
\s Mwari anoonekwa pamabasa ake makuru sepakutinhira nemheni
\p
\v 1 Uye nekuda kweizvi moyo wangu unobvunda uye unouruka kubva panzvimbo yawo.
\v 2 Inzwa zvekunzwa mutinhiro weinzwi rake, hongu ruzha rwunobva mumuromo make rwunobuda.
\v 3 Anoururamisira pasi pematenga ese, nechiedza chake pamusoro pemigumo yenyika.
\v 4 Shure kweizvi kunoomba inzwi, anotinhira neinzwi reukuru hwake uye haazvidzivisi panonzwikwa inzwi rake.
\v 5 Mwari anotinhira nenzwi rake zvinoshamisa; anoita zvinhu zvikuru zvatisingagoni kunzwisisa.
\v 6 Nokuti anoti kumagada echando: Chivai panyika; saizvozvo kumvura yekupfunha, uye kumvura huru yesimba rake.
\v 7 Anonamatidza ruoko rwemunhu umwe neumwe, kuti vazive vanhu vese vebasa rake.
\v 8 Zvino mhuka dzinopinda mumagara ndokurambira munzvimbo dzadzo.
\v 9 Dutu remhepo rinobuda pakamuri \add rekuchamhembe\add*; nechando kumhepo dzekumaodzanyemba.
\v 10 Chando chakachena chinopiwa nemweya waMwari, uye mvura mhami inogwamba.
\v 11 Hongu, neunyoro anozadza gore uye anoparadzira gore nekupenya kwake.
\v 12 Uye rinotendeudzwa nekunangisa kwake, kuti zviite zvese zvaanozviraira pamusoro pechiso chevhu repanyika.
\v 13 Kungava neshamhu, kungava nenyika yake, kana netsitsi dzake anozvisvikisa.
\p
\v 14 Teerera kune izvi, haiwa Jobho; mira, ugorangarira mabasa anoshamisa aMwari.
\v 15 Unoziva here kuti Mwari anoagadzira rinhi, apenyese chiedza chegore?
\v 16 Unoziva here kuremberedzwa kwemakore, zvishamiso zvewakaperera paruzivo?
\v 17 Kuti nguvo dzako dzinodziya sei, pakunyaradza kwenyika ne\add mhepo\add* yekuchamhembe?
\v 18 Wakaradanura here gore pamwe naye, asimbe sechionioni chakaumbwa nekunyunguduswa?
\p
\v 19 Tidzidzisezvatichareva kwaari, hatingagadziri \add chinhu\add* nokuda kwerima.
\v 20 Zvingatsanangurwa kwaari here kuti ndinotaura? Zvirokwazvo kana munhu akataura achamedzwa?
\v 21 Zvino ikozvino havaoni chiedza chinopenya chiri mumakore, uye mhepo painopfuura inoachenesa.
\v 22 Goridhe rinobva ku. Kuna Mwari kune umambo hunotyisa.
\v 23 Wemasimbaose hatigoni kumuwana; wakakwirira pasimba nepamutongo, haamanikidzi, uye mukuru pakururama.
\v 24 Naizvozvo vanhu vanomutya; haana hanya nnevakachenjera pamoyo.
